headline: Want an Extra $1,000 of Dividend Income in 2025? Invest $11,400 in These 3 High-Yield Stocks.
summary: If you're trying to secure a stream of passive income to support your retirement dreams, there's more than one way to make it happen.  Buying rental properties is an easy-to-understand option you're probably already familiar with.  Unfortunately, owning rental properties comes with day-to-day responsibilities that most retirees would rather avoid.
